{"tid":1120351,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"斯里蘭卡又爆炸","createTime":"2019-04-22T15:04:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-22T15:35:02.000Z","uid":117200,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a43abea6726400acc09fe34e8480e204ddf485a6","tid":1120351,"uid":117200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T15:04:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.rti.org.tw/assets/thumbnails/2019/04/21/de0a9a54387bda79648a67c464757b08.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.rti.org.tw%2Fassets%2Fthumbnails%2F2019%2F04%2F21%2Fde0a9a54387bda79648a67c464757b08.jpg&h=ea1ec80d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n斯里蘭卡首都科倫坡再發生爆炸。一段由英國《衛報》記者於社交網絡上載的片段見到，民眾於當地一間教堂附近逃生。這名記者表示，爆炸是於教堂外發生，形容是小爆炸。而這間教堂是昨日被襲擊的目標之一。<br />\n<br />\n另外，斯里蘭卡警方於當地一個私營巴士站，搜獲87個較低爆炸力的引爆器。<br />\n<br />\n昨日的連環爆炸增至290人死亡、超過500人受傷，當局至今拘捕24名疑犯。斯里蘭卡政府宣布，由午夜起實施緊急狀態，批准警方、陸軍、海軍和空軍，採取特別措施保障公眾安全。政府內閣發言人表示，相信是當地一個知名度較低的伊斯蘭極端組織策劃今次襲擊，亦懷疑組織與外國有聯繫。"},{"pid":"65aa92d4f1689d1d15eb55f0d74d15eee18494b6","tid":1120351,"uid":151695,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T15:05:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">BOOM</span></span>"},{"pid":"3fe43c864ff35b2f6bb0c5d2295da619407a025f","tid":1120351,"uid":93479,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T15:06:37.000Z","msg":"都反映左當地警力，歐洲起碼一爆就追人<br />\n迫到人哋逃亡<br />\n<br />\n今天都仲夠膽繼續炸"},{"pid":"c1cb70a1c8ca1351d7463ee55b6160253db86463","tid":1120351,"uid":220431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T15:11:36.000Z","msg":"翻閹咁撚賤"},{"pid":"35dc53fafc2ce5ac525729d406b4dc8c9403acca","tid":1120351,"uid":35815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T15:12:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"91e8de8d252da96ba5cfd9af080b8fef7e060008","tid":1120351,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T15:32:48.000Z","msg":"拿,等連登牧師入來傳耶道"},{"pid":"631804af563febc5aef9e52afa22eb4c23d054f1","tid":1120351,"uid":987,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T15:35:02.000Z","msg":"搵中共幫手啦"}]}